Project Gumby
 - iBetu prototype

 People will be able to 
  - Sign up 
  - Log in

  Once logged in they can
  - Create an "Offer" 
  - View all existing "Offers"
  - Make a bet on an "Offer"

  Offer
  An offer is all the terms of the bet. In normal betting situation it would be seen as West coast eagles are paying $2.30 to beat Geelong on said date

  Bet
  A bet is when someone takes on an offer and places and financial transaction to it. 

The Prototype
 - Will be web based
 - Using firebase to handle user log ins and sign ups
 - Will integrate with a blockchain TBA
 - Will not be tested against a wide range of mobile decives

 